{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"span":4,"markdown":"ANC1 visits were consistently above expectations in 2025, averaging ~26,900 per month vs. ~24,200 expected (~11% higher), with June 2025 ~26,200 visits (~9% above expected), and a smaller but still positive surplus again in September 2025, when ANC1 remained above expected levels.

ANC4 visits stayed close to expected levels, averaging ~19,300 per month vs. ~18,800 expected (~3% higher), with June 2025 ~18,900 visits (~5% above expected).

